Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.93,0:00:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Suigetsu... I will release you from\N{\i1}this place some day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.12,0:00:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it was you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.75,0:00:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that you're here must mean\Nyou killed Orochimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.98,0:00:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.62,0:00:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But never mind that.\NLet's get you out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.49,0:00:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Free at last. Thank you, Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.71,0:01:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Suigetsu, you're the first.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.52,0:01:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.09,0:01:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, first? There are others then?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.32,0:01:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Two others. I'm taking Jugo from the northern\N hideout and Karin from the southern hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.72,0:01:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.95,0:01:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.45,0:01:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing...\NJust that I don't like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.52,0:01:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get along with them...\NAt least, that's what I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.85,0:01:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, you picked me, but I wonder\N about choosing those two, Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.62,0:01:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough with the rambling.\NPut on your clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.00,0:01:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.63,0:01:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ordering me around like a big shot, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.25,0:01:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me clarify the relationship\Nbetween you and me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.39,0:01:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.09,0:02:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but you {\i1}chose{\i0} to rescue me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.69,0:02:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I never said anything about following you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.15,0:02:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because you defeated Orochimaru\Ndoesn't make you better than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.20,0:02:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone was after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.85,0:02:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You were Orochimaru's pet, so you weren't\N imprisoned and you stayed by his side.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.84,0:02:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You had more chances to kill him\Nthan the rest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.22,0:02:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha... Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.27,0:02:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But I let you go just now,\Nso that makes us even.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.83,0:02:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm free at last,\Nso I'm going to do as I please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.57,0:02:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.42,0:03:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.54,0:03:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.35,0:03:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It was your team, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.12,0:03:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The team that brought down\Nmy great predecessor, Zabuza Momochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.14,0:03:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever happened to his blade...\Nthe Executioner's Blade?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.12,0:03:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.42,0:03:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If you tell me where the blade is,\N and I take possession of it, then I'll be willing to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.25,0:03:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Put some clothes on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:20.17,Title,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(736.875,586.25)}Zabuza's Blade\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.80,0:05:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,GREAT NARUTO BRIDGE
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.85,0:05:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The Great Naruto Bridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.98,0:05:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What a weird name...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.92,0:05:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, was the great Zabuza Senpai strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.63,0:05:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyone, duck!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.06,0:06:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not that naïve!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.52,0:06:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kakashi Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.00,0:06:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Guys like you aren't called "Ninja"...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.59,0:06:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just mere kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.47,0:06:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Sasuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.34,0:06:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.26,0:06:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.59,0:06:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.85,0:07:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Sasuke, are you sure it was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.88,0:07:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.04,0:07:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not here. I wonder why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How would I know?\NI'm not the keeper of that grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.83,0:07:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's not there,\Nsomeone must've taken it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.37,0:07:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right about that.\NIt wouldn't have walked off on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.85,0:07:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.04,0:07:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but without the blade here,\Nme joining you will have to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What'll you do then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.14,0:07:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What else? I'm gonna look for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.92,0:07:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The blade of the Seven Ninja Swords Men of the Mist was passed down from generation to generation. That was the system.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.95,0:07:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I aspired to become one of them\Nand trained for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.75,0:07:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Since Zabuza Senpai is gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.41,0:07:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who should possess\Nthat Executioner's Blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.35,0:07:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch where you're walking, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.99,0:08:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.85,0:08:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You have a problem, Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.35,0:08:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.93,0:08:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.76,0:08:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What's his problem, stupid...\Njerk... old fart... idiot...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.04,0:08:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so nice, Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.99,0:08:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So...how're you gonna settle this debt?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.83,0:08:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.00,0:08:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This yogurt is the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.22,0:08:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been so long since\NI had anything like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.86,0:08:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in a water tank all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.80,0:08:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you afford to relax like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.07,0:08:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But...you're the one in a rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.21,0:08:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why're you gathering us\Ntogether anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.15,0:08:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you when we've all assembled.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.39,0:08:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,"All right, let's go conquer this world!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.85,0:09:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not gonna say something\Nlike that, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.55,0:09:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Do that on your own time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm aiming for...\Nsomething much bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.45,0:09:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If anyone else started saying that,\NI wouldn't believe it for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.05,0:09:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.32,0:09:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I think maybe it's possible...\NAnd that's the strange thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.75,0:09:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh say...\NThe Great Naruto Bridge, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.55,0:09:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever heard of a large blade\Nnear that bridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.08,0:09:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... Oh, maybe there was...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.68,0:09:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.14,0:09:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He's looking for that blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.91,0:09:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! S-Someone might know about it...\NI'll go and ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.52,0:09:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.03,0:09:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're quite the ladies' man, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.35,0:09:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.12,0:09:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- Tazuna...\N- Who lives by the riverside...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.74,0:09:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...would know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.89,0:10:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Tazuna...huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.99,0:10:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is this Tazuna?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.15,0:10:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The carpenter boss who built that bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.99,0:10:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The boss isn't here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.22,0:10:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know where he went?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.59,0:10:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,To the Land of Lightning to build a bridge.\NHe took Inari with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.24,0:10:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He won't be back for another year.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.75,0:10:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The Land of Lightning, eh?\NThat's very far.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.42,0:10:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know of a large blade that\Nwas left near the Great Naruto Bridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.82,0:10:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.15,0:10:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenzen Daikoku took it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.29,0:10:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He originally came here to capture\Nthe Ninja who wielded the blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But after learning the Ninja was dead,\Nhe took the blade with him instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.55,0:10:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it... Tenzen Daikoku, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.72,0:11:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He was the aide to\Nthe lord of the Land of Water.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.08,0:11:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, many of his men were killed during\N Zabuza Senpai's coup d'état in the Hidden Mist.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess he had a grudge from back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.57,0:11:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Where the hell...\Ndo you think you're--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.65,0:11:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, we were just looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.45,0:11:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Who are you guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.01,0:11:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem like the type to know\Nall kinds of things...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.14,0:11:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I know nothing about Tenzen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything will do.\NJust tell us what you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.05,0:11:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Tenzen Daikoku is a politician...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.24,0:11:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's another side to him.\N He's the boss of a huge band of thieves.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.19,0:11:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear he doles out huge bribes to the feudal lords,\N and gets to do whatever evil things he likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.42,0:11:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,See, you know it all. And?\NWhere does he live?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.74,0:12:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Just to the south...\Nthere's a castle in the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Rumor says several thousand mercenaries\Nguard the place and that it's impenetrable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.43,0:12:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Who's there? How did you get in?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The day after tomorrow, this castle will be\N attacked by tens of thousands of soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.07,0:12:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you gather\Nevery man available.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.40,0:12:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,My name...is Suigetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.20,0:12:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,An intruder! Men! Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.87,0:12:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Cripes... What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.63,0:13:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems another powerful clan plans\Nto attack Tenzen's castle tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.68,0:13:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,with an army that numbers\Nin the tens of thousands.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.31,0:13:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.60,0:13:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.19,0:13:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The more confused the enemy becomes,\Nthe better my chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.11,0:13:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Be it several thousand or tens of thousands,\N it doesn't matter to a Ninja like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.07,0:13:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll sneak in tonight and\Ntake the Executioner's Blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.13,0:13:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,How about making a wager?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.12,0:13:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A wager...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.13,0:13:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,On who gets\Nthe Executioner's Blade first...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.05,0:13:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! I never expected you\Nto have a playful side!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.34,0:13:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it. It sounds like fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.13,0:13:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it starts now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.06,0:13:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one rule.\NWe don't kill anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.45,0:13:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.89,0:13:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.31,0:13:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.04,0:14:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean... Now as in...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.03,0:14:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It really starts now, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.46,0:14:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't lose this wager.\NWell, all right, let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fire Style: Fireball Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.09,0:14:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta hand it to you, Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.16,0:14:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What the--?! He's gone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.99,0:14:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this for real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.99,0:14:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, may as well get started!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.35,0:16:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This is tiring, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.69,0:16:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, my goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.83,0:16:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible... You defeated\Nall those men by yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.53,0:16:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well yeah. Even with legitimate weapons,\Nattacking me is useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.95,0:16:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If legitimate weapons are of no use...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.23,0:16:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How about...this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, that's my Executioner's Blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.34,0:16:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.35,0:16:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You let down your guard at the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.97,0:16:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. Blades don't work on me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.99,0:16:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.30,0:16:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.11,0:16:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're able to wield that blade\Nwithout any special training...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.84,0:16:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It helps when you have a good physique.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear you've been telling\Neveryone in town...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.03,0:17:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That you killed the Demon Zabuza\Nand took that blade from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.36,0:17:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That wasn't me...\NIt was Lord Tenzen who...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.78,0:17:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... So you killed Zabuza Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.51,0:17:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No... The one who killed Zabuza was...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.47,0:17:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Zabuza?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.18,0:17:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Err...no! The one who killed Mr. Zabuza\Nwasn't me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.53,0:17:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...the one...from yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.63,0:17:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the one!\NHe's the one who killed Mr. Zabuza!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.43,0:17:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,All I did was bring the blade\Nback from the grave!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.88,0:17:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you some points for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.17,0:17:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a pretty good lie for a villain\Nlike you to come up with.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.55,0:17:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Suigetsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.51,0:18:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,How thoughtful.\NI was feeling a bit dehydrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.02,0:18:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you're under the wrong impression here.\N I wasn't particularly close to Mr. Zabuza.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But the thought of my Senpai\Nfrom my village...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.53,0:18:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...having such pathetic rumors about\Nlosing to weaklings like you is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.79,0:18:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You know...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.59,0:18:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Do you think you can\Nget away with this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.47,0:18:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you'll have to pay for this...right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.56,0:18:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'll test it on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.63,0:18:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it. What's the sense\Nin killing someone like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.99,0:18:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I've cut through the main pillars,\Nso you'd better get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.28,0:19:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll spare your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.08,0:19:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of respect for you, Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.58,0:19:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke? Not that...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.21,0:19:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke who killed Orochimaru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.43,0:19:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, you're famous.\NThey know your name even around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.48,0:19:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I have this blade,\NI won't even lose to you...maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.47,0:19:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Say... You knew that I was going\Nto claim this blade, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.70,0:19:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And...You knew from the start\Nthat the blade wasn't in that grave...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.95,0:19:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.68,0:19:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who warned that castle\Nto gather its men...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.54,0:19:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,was you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.65,0:19:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenzen acted like he'd met you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.06,0:20:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey? Did you suggest a wager just\Nto lure me into enemy territory?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.13,0:20:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you just testing me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.90,0:20:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, you're terrible.\NWhat if I was hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.89,0:20:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I understand now...\Nwhat kind of guy you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.07,0:20:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're exactly the way\NI imagined you to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.53,0:20:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I have my blade.\NSo I'll help you as promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So? Which way do we go? Oh wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.53,0:20:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The nearest route, right?\NThat would be your answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.33,0:20:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm starting to figure you out...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.35,0:20:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, the nearest route.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.03,0:20:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because Orochimaru\Nis dead doesn't mean
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.28,0:20:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you have your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.23,0:21:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The feeling of this Chakra...\N{\i1}I-It can't be...
